\begin_layout Section
习题
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
1.
 pf.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
用归纳法, 当点数
\begin_inset Formula $v(T)=1$
\end_inset

时, 问题显然成立.
 假设
\begin_inset Formula $v(T)=n$
\end_inset

时命题成立.
 现在考虑
\begin_inset Formula $v(T)=n+1$
\end_inset

的情况.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由于
\begin_inset Formula $T$
\end_inset

是树, 所以必然存在顶点的度数为
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

, 否则任取一点
\begin_inset Formula $v_{1}$
\end_inset

染色, 并从
\begin_inset Formula $v_{1}$
\end_inset

发出的线中任取一条边
\begin_inset Formula $e_{1}$
\end_inset

, 它连接的顶点记为
\begin_inset Formula $v_{2}$
\end_inset

, 并对
\begin_inset Formula $v_{2}$
\end_inset

染色, 如果
\begin_inset Formula $v_{2}$
\end_inset

的度至少是
\begin_inset Formula $2$
\end_inset

, 则除了
\begin_inset Formula $e_{1}$
\end_inset

外还有另一条边
\begin_inset Formula $e_{2}$
\end_inset

, 如此下去, 由于图的顶点数有限, 这种取法必然在有限步内到达一个已经被染色的顶点
\begin_inset Formula $v_{i}$
\end_inset

, 这与树是无环图矛盾.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
取
\begin_inset Formula $T$
\end_inset

的度数为
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

的顶点
\begin_inset Formula $v$
\end_inset

, 从树中去掉这个顶点以及唯一与其相连接的边后形成图
\begin_inset Formula $T'$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula $v(T')=n$
\end_inset

, 由归纳假设
\begin_inset Formula $v(T')-e(T')=1$
\end_inset

, 而
\begin_inset Formula $v(T)=v(T')+1$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $e(T)=e(T')+1$
\end_inset

.
 即得
\begin_inset Formula $v(T)-e(T)=1$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
1.
 pf2
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
可以对边数使用归纳法, 从树
\begin_inset Formula $T$
\end_inset

中去掉一条边, 则将原来的树分成两个子树
\begin_inset Formula $T_{1}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $T_{2}$
\end_inset

, 从而
\begin_inset Formula $v(T)=v(T_{1})+v(T_{2})$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $e(T)=e(T_{1})+e(T_{2})+1$
\end_inset

, 所以
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
v(T)-e(T)=v(T_{1})+v(T_{2})-e(T_{1})-e(T_{2})-1=1.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
2.
 pf
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
本题条件中的图精确来说是指连通图.
 由第1题的结论, 已经证明了当
\begin_inset Formula $\Gamma$
\end_inset

是树时, 有
\begin_inset Formula $v(\Gamma)-e(\Gamma)=1$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由于任何连通图
\begin_inset Formula $\Gamma$
\end_inset

都包含一个树
\begin_inset Formula $T$
\end_inset

, 而
\begin_inset Formula $v(\Gamma)=v(T)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $e(\Gamma)\ge e(T)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
v(\Gamma)-e(\Gamma)\le v(T)-e(T)=1.
\]

\end_inset

当
\begin_inset Formula $v(\Gamma)-e(\Gamma)=1$
\end_inset

时, 必然有一个点的度数是
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

, 否则由于每条边有两个顶点, 当统计边的总数时同时统计连接的两个点, 则统计出的点数(重复计数统计)恰好是边数的两倍, 也恰好是所有顶点的度数之和,
 即如果记
\begin_inset Formula $d(v)$
\end_inset

为顶点
\begin_inset Formula $v$
\end_inset

的度数, 有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sum d(v_{i})=2e(\Gamma)\ge2v(\Gamma)=2e(\Gamma)+2,
\]

\end_inset

矛盾.
 如果点
\begin_inset Formula $v_{1}$
\end_inset

的度数是
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

, 则可从
\begin_inset Formula $\Gamma$
\end_inset

中除去这个点和它发出的边, 然后根据归纳法可得
\begin_inset Formula $\Gamma$
\end_inset

是一棵树.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
3.
 pf
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
题目中的图
\begin_inset Formula $\Gamma$
\end_inset

是连通图.
 可以考虑树的生长过程, 任取一点
\begin_inset Formula $v_{1}$
\end_inset

, 设
\begin_inset Formula $A=\left\{ v_{1}\right\} $
\end_inset

.
 由于图是连通图, 且
\begin_inset Formula $v_{1}$
\end_inset

有出度.
 所以可以将
\begin_inset Formula $\Gamma$
\end_inset

中与
\begin_inset Formula $v_{1}$
\end_inset

距离是
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

的所有顶点放入
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

中, 并将连接到
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

中点的边染色.
 由于
\begin_inset Formula $\Gamma$
\end_inset

的连通性, 从
\begin_inset Formula $\Gamma$
\end_inset

中又可找到与
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

距离是
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

的顶点, 将其放入
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

中, 并将连接到
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

中的边中任取一条染色.
 如此继续下去直到
\begin_inset Formula $\Gamma$
\end_inset

中的所有顶点都放入
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

中, 则染色的边与顶点
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

形成一棵树.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
6.
 pf
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由于一条边由两个面所共用, 所以
\begin_inset Formula $fp=2e$
\end_inset

.
 由于一个顶点发出
\begin_inset Formula $q$
\end_inset

条边, 一条边由两个顶点组成, 所以
\begin_inset Formula $vq=2e$
\end_inset

即得.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
8.pf
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $v-e+f=-2$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
10.pf
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{1}{2}+\frac{1}{\pi}\arctan x:\RR\to(0,1)$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Note Note
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
TODO
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Chapter
连续性
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
开集与闭集
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

为拓扑空间, 
\begin_inset Formula $O\subseteq X$
\end_inset

, 若
\begin_inset Formula $O$
\end_inset

是它自己每个点的邻域, 则称
\begin_inset Formula $O$
\end_inset

为
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

的开集.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Box ovalbox
position "t"
hor_pos "c"
has_inner_box 1
inner_pos "t"
use_parbox 0
use_makebox 0
width "100col%"
special "none"
height "1in"
height_special "totalheight"
thickness "0.4pt"
separation "3pt"
shadowsize "4pt"
framecolor "black"
backgroundcolor "none"
status open

\begin_layout Paragraph
定义1.3.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

是一个集合, 
\begin_inset Formula $\forall x\in X$
\end_inset

, 取以
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

的子集为元素的集族, 这集族若满足以下条件, 则集族中的每个元素称为
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

的一个邻域.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Argument item:1
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
(a)
\end_layout

\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

在它自己的每个邻域内;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Argument item:1
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
(b)
\end_layout

\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

的任两个邻域的交集为
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

的一个邻域;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Argument item:1
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
(c)
\end_layout

\end_inset

 若
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

的邻域, 且
\begin_inset Formula $N\subseteq U\subseteq X$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula $U$
\end_inset

也是
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

的邻域;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Argument item:1
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
(d)
\end_layout

\end_inset

 若
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

的邻域, 且若
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
N^{\circ}=\left\{ z\in N\mid N\text{ 是 }z\text{ 的邻域}\right\} ,
\]

\end_inset

则
\begin_inset Formula $N^{\circ}$
\end_inset

也是
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

的邻域.
 (集合
\begin_inset Formula $N^{\circ}$
\end_inset

叫作
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

的内部)
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
注: 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
(c)推出: 任一组开集的并是开集;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
(b)推出: 有限多个开集的交为开集;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
整个空间
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\varnothing$
\end_inset

是开集;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
(d)推出: 对于点
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

的邻域, 
\begin_inset Formula $N^{\circ}$
\end_inset

是开集, 
\begin_inset Formula $x\in N^{\circ}$
\end_inset

且
\begin_inset Formula $N^{\circ}\subseteq N$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由此, 可以将上面的拓扑定义改为以下形式:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
定义:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
若对集合
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

给定一组子集叫做开集, 满足以下结构的
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

与子集族一起使
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

称为一个拓扑空间.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
任意多个开集的并集是开集;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
任意有限多个开集的交集是开集;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

与
\begin_inset Formula $\varnothing$
\end_inset

也是开集;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $\forall x\in X$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $N\subseteq X$
\end_inset

, 若有开集
\begin_inset Formula $O$
\end_inset

, 使
\begin_inset Formula $x\in O\subseteq N$
\end_inset

, 则称
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

为
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

的邻域.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
其中上面最后一条作为邻域的定义.
 配备以上结构的集合
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

叫做一个拓扑空间.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
定义:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
若
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

是拓扑空间, 
\begin_inset Formula $Y\subseteq X$
\end_inset

, 若以
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

的开集与
\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset

的交集作为
\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset

中开集, 则称为
\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset

上的诱导拓扑.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
其他定义有离散拓扑, 离散空间; 余有限拓扑(含
\begin_inset Formula $\varnothing$
\end_inset

); 闭集, 极限点或聚点, 闭包(
\begin_inset Formula $\overline{A}$
\end_inset

), 稠密集.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
Thm 2.2.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
一个子集是闭集当且仅当它包含自己的所有极限点.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Box Boxed
position "t"
hor_pos "c"
has_inner_box 1
inner_pos "t"
use_parbox 0
use_makebox 0
width "100col%"
special "none"
height "1in"
height_special "totalheight"
thickness "0.4pt"
separation "3pt"
shadowsize "4pt"
framecolor "black"
backgroundcolor "none"
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
pf.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
\begin_inset Formula $\Longrightarrow$
\end_inset

: 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

闭, 则
\begin_inset Formula $A^{c}$
\end_inset

开, 故
\begin_inset Formula $\forall x\in A^{c}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

不是
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

的极限点.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
故
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

包含了自己所有极限点.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
\begin_inset Formula $\Longleftarrow$
\end_inset

: 若包含了自己的所有极限点, 即
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
\begin_inset Formula $\forall x\in A^{c}$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

不是
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

的极限点, 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
则有
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

的邻域
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

与
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

不交.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
故
\begin_inset Formula $N\subseteq A^{c}$
\end_inset

, 即
\begin_inset Formula $A^{c}$
\end_inset

是它自己每点的邻域.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
故
\begin_inset Formula $A^{c}$
\end_inset

开, 即
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

闭.
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
Thm.
 2.3.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

的闭包是最小的包含
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

的闭集, 即是包含
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

的一切闭集的交.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Box Boxed
position "t"
hor_pos "c"
has_inner_box 1
inner_pos "t"
use_parbox 0
use_makebox 0
width "100col%"
special "none"
height "1in"
height_special "totalheight"
thickness "0.4pt"
separation "3pt"
shadowsize "4pt"
framecolor "black"
backgroundcolor "none"
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
pf.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
\begin_inset Formula $\overline{A}=A\cup A'$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
1).
 
\begin_inset Formula $\overline{A}$
\end_inset

闭
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
若
\begin_inset Formula $x\in\overline{A}^{c}$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

不是
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

的极限点.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
存在
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

的开邻域
\begin_inset Formula $U_{x}$
\end_inset

使得
\begin_inset Formula $U_{x}\cap A=\varnothing$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
由开集是它每个点的邻域, 故
\begin_inset Formula $U_{x}\cap A'=\varnothing$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
即
\begin_inset Formula $U_{x}\cap\overline{A}=\varnothing$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
由于
\begin_inset Formula $\forall x\in\overline{A}^{c}$
\end_inset

, 存在开集
\begin_inset Formula $U_{x}$
\end_inset

使
\begin_inset Formula $U_{x}\subseteq\overline{A}^{c}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
故
\begin_inset Formula $\overline{A}^{c}$
\end_inset

开, 所以
\begin_inset Formula $\overline{A}$
\end_inset

闭.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
2).
 若闭集
\begin_inset Formula $B\supseteq A$
\end_inset

, 则由Thm2.2.
 
\begin_inset Formula $B\supseteq B'\supseteq A'$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
故
\begin_inset Formula $B\supseteq\overline{A}\supseteq A$
\end_inset

, 即任何包含
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

的闭集也包含
\begin_inset Formula $\overline{A}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
Thm.
 2.4.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
一个集合为闭集当且仅当它等于自己的闭包.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
定义:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
集合
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

的背部是包含于
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

的所有开集之并, 记作
\begin_inset Formula $A^{\circ}$
\end_inset

:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
点
\begin_inset Formula $x\in A^{\circ}$
\end_inset

当且仅当
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

的邻域;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
开集是它自己的内部.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
集合
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

的边界定义为
\begin_inset Formula $\overline{A}\cap\overline{A^{c}}=\left(A^{\circ}\cup A^{c\circ}\right)^{c}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Box Boxed
position "t"
hor_pos "c"
has_inner_box 1
inner_pos "t"
use_parbox 0
use_makebox 0
width "100col%"
special "none"
height "1in"
height_special "totalheight"
thickness "0.4pt"
separation "3pt"
shadowsize "4pt"
framecolor "black"
backgroundcolor "none"
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(A^{\circ}\cup A^{c\circ}\right)^{c}=A^{\circ c}\cap A^{c\circ c}=A^{cc\circ c}\cap A^{c\circ c}=\overline{A^{c}}\cap\overline{A}.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
一个子集的边界可以是整个空间, 如
\begin_inset Formula $\QQ^{3}\subseteq E^{3}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设集合
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

上有一个拓扑, 
\begin_inset Formula $\beta$
\end_inset

为这个拓扑的一组开集, 使得每个开集可写成
\begin_inset Formula $\beta$
\end_inset

中成员的并集, 则
\begin_inset Formula $\beta$
\end_inset

称为此拓扑的一组拓扑基.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
Thm.
 2.5.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $\beta$
\end_inset

是由
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

的子集构成的一个非空组, 若
\begin_inset Formula $\beta$
\end_inset

内有限多个成员的交仍属于
\begin_inset Formula $\beta$
\end_inset

, 并且若
\begin_inset Formula $\cup\beta=X$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula $\beta$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

上某个拓扑的拓扑基.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
pf.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
取
\begin_inset Formula $\beta$
\end_inset

中元素的所有可能的并集作为开集, 它形成一个拓扑.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
习题
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
连续映射
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
Thm 2.6.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $X,Y$
\end_inset

是拓扑空间, 从
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

到
\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset

的映射连续当且仅当
\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset

的每个开集的原像是
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

中的开集.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
此定理依赖的映射连续的定义是: 
\begin_inset Formula $\forall x\in X$
\end_inset

, 对于任意的
\begin_inset Formula $f(x)$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset

中的邻域
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

, 集合
\begin_inset Formula $f^{-1}(N)$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

内的邻域.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
或者简而言之: 邻域的原像是邻域.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
Thm.
 2.7.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
连续函数的复合是连续函数.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
pf.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $f:X\to Y$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $g:Y\to Z$
\end_inset

均连续.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $O$
\end_inset

为
\begin_inset Formula $Z$
\end_inset

内开集, 并由
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(g\circ f\right)^{-1}(O)=f^{-1}\left(g^{-1}(O)\right).
\]

\end_inset

由
\begin_inset Formula $g$
\end_inset

连续, 
\begin_inset Formula $g^{-1}(O)$
\end_inset

为
\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset

中开集.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

连续, 
\begin_inset Formula $f^{-1}\left(g^{-1}(O)\right)$
\end_inset

为
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

中开集.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
Thm.
 2.8.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $f:X\to Y$
\end_inset

连续, 且
\begin_inset Formula $A\subseteq X$
\end_inset

有子空间拓扑.
 则限制映射
\begin_inset Formula $f\mid_{A}:A\to Y$
\end_inset

连续.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
pf.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $O$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset

中开集, 由
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(f\mid_{A}\right)^{-1}(O)=A\cap f^{-1}(O).
\]

\end_inset

由
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

连续, 所以
\begin_inset Formula $f^{-1}(O)$
\end_inset

为
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

中开集.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
所以
\begin_inset Formula $A\cap f^{-1}(O)$
\end_inset

为
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

中开集.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
所以
\begin_inset Formula $f\mid_{A}$
\end_inset

连续.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
其它术语定义: 恒等映射, 含入映射:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
若
\begin_inset Formula $A\subseteq X$
\end_inset

, 映射
\begin_inset Formula $i:A\to X$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $x\mapsto x$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula $i$
\end_inset

称为含入映射.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
Thm.
 2.9.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
以下各条相互等价:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
(a).
 
\begin_inset Formula $f:X\to Y$
\end_inset

是连续映射;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
(b).
 若
\begin_inset Formula $\beta$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset

的一组拓扑基, 
\begin_inset Formula $\beta$
\end_inset

内每个成员的原像为
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

的开集;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
(c).
 
\begin_inset Formula $\forall A\subseteq X$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $f(\overline{A})\subseteq\overline{f(A)}$
\end_inset

;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
(d).
 
\begin_inset Formula $\forall B\subseteq Y$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\overline{f^{-1}(B)}\subseteq f^{-1}(\overline{B})$
\end_inset

;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
(e).
 
\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset

内任何闭集的原像是
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

的闭集.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
pf: 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
(b)
\begin_inset Formula $\Longrightarrow$
\end_inset

(c):
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $A\subseteq X$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula $f(A)\subseteq\overline{f(A)}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
若
\begin_inset Formula $x\in\overline{A}\setminus A$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula $f(x)$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $f(A)$
\end_inset

的极限点.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $f(x)$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset

内的邻域, 则有
\begin_inset Formula $\beta$
\end_inset

内的开集
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

, 使得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f(x)\in B\subseteq N.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由(b), 
\begin_inset Formula $f^{-1}(B)$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

中开, 是
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

的邻域.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

的极限点, 则
\begin_inset Formula $\left(f^{-1}(B)\setminus\left\{ x\right\} \right)\cap A\ne\varnothing$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
故
\begin_inset Formula $\left(B\setminus\left\{ f(x)\right\} \right)\cap f(A)\ne\varnothing$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
从而有
\begin_inset Formula $\left(N\setminus\left\{ f(x)\right\} \right)\cap f(A)\ne\varnothing$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
(d)
\begin_inset Formula $\Longrightarrow$
\end_inset

(e)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset

中闭集, 则
\begin_inset Formula $\overline{B}=B$
\end_inset

, 由(d),
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\overline{f^{-1}(B)}\subseteq f^{-1}(\overline{B})=f^{-1}(B).
\]

\end_inset

故
\begin_inset Formula $f^{-1}(B)$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

中闭.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
一个反例:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
存在双射
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

, 使得
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

连续, 但
\begin_inset Formula $f^{-1}$
\end_inset

不连续.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
Hint:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $C$
\end_inset

为复平面上的单位圆周,
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
则
\begin_inset Formula $f(x):[0,1)\to C$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $x\mapsto\ue^{2\pi\ui x}$
\end_inset

连续.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
但
\begin_inset Formula $f^{-1}$
\end_inset

不连续, 因为开集
\begin_inset Formula $[0,1)$
\end_inset

的原像
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(f^{-1}\right)^{-1}\left([0,1)\right)
\]

\end_inset

不是
\begin_inset Formula $C$
\end_inset

中开集.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
定义:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
一个同胚
\begin_inset Formula $h:X\to Y$
\end_inset

是指一个连续双射, 其逆映射也连续.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
圆盘是同胚于
\begin_inset Formula $E^{2}$
\end_inset

内单位闭圆盘
\begin_inset Formula $D$
\end_inset

的任何拓扑空间, 令
\begin_inset Formula $C$
\end_inset

为单位圆周, 若
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

为圆盘, 
\begin_inset Formula $h:A\to D$
\end_inset

为同胚映射, 则
\begin_inset Formula $h^{-1}(C)$
\end_inset

称为
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

的边界, 记为
\begin_inset Formula $\partial A$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
Lem.
 2.10.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
圆盘边界到自身的任何同胚可扩张成圆盘自身的同胚.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
pf.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

是圆盘, 取同胚映射
\begin_inset Formula $h:A\to D$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设同胚映射
\begin_inset Formula $g:\partial A\to\partial A$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
则
\begin_inset Formula $f:D\to D$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $x\mapsto\norm{x}h\circ g\circ h^{-1}\left(\frac{x}{\norm{x}}\right)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $x\ne0$
\end_inset

.
 额外定义
\begin_inset Formula $f(0)=0$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
即是
\begin_inset Formula $D$
\end_inset

的自同胚, 这个扩张
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

称为辅式扩张.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
Lem.
 2.11.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

与
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

为沿着边界弧相交的两个圆盘, 则
\begin_inset Formula $A\cup B$
\end_inset

为圆盘.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
注: 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

与
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

的交集边界弧是连通的, 否则有下图作为反例.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Graphics
	filename Basic Topology - Armstrong/已粘贴2.png
	width 5cm

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
习题
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
充满空间的曲线
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
维数作为参数表示所需的最少个数并不妥当.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Graphics
	filename Basic Topology - Armstrong/已粘贴3.png
	width 5cm

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
习题
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
Tietze扩张定理
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
反例:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

是拓扑空间, 
\begin_inset Formula $A\subseteq X$
\end_inset

为子拓扑空间, 存在
\begin_inset Formula $f:A\to\RR$
\end_inset

连续, 但
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

不能连续扩张到
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

中.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
比如:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $A=(0,1)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $X=[0,1]$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $f:A\to E^{1}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $x\mapsto\ln\frac{x}{1-x}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
定义2.12.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
集合 
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

 上的一个度量或距离函数是定义在笛卡尔积 
\begin_inset Formula $X\times X$
\end_inset

 上的一个实值函数 
\begin_inset Formula $d$
\end_inset

, 它对于任意 
\begin_inset Formula $x,y,z\in X$
\end_inset

 满足: 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
(a).
 
\begin_inset Formula $d(x,y)\ge0$
\end_inset

, 等号成立, 当且仅当 
\begin_inset Formula $x=y$
\end_inset

;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
(b).
 
\begin_inset Formula $d(x,y)=d(y,x)$
\end_inset

; 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
(c).
 
\begin_inset Formula $d(x,y)+d(y,z)\ge d(x,z)$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
集合具备了一个度量, 以后叫作度量空间.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
Lem.
 2.13
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $d$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

上的度量, 
\begin_inset Formula $A\subseteq X$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $d(x,A)=\inf_{a\in A}d(x,a)$
\end_inset

, 则实值函数
\begin_inset Formula $x\mapsto d(x,A)$
\end_inset

是连续的.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
pf.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $x\in X$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $d=d(x,A)$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $\RR$
\end_inset

上的邻域.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $f:X\to\RR$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $x\mapsto d(x,A)$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
以下证明
\begin_inset Formula $f^{-1}(N)$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

的邻域, 即:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
若
\begin_inset Formula $\epsilon>0$
\end_inset

适当小, 使
\begin_inset Formula $(d-\epsilon,d+\epsilon)\subseteq N$
\end_inset

, 只要证
\begin_inset Formula $f^{-1}(d-\epsilon,d+\epsilon)$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

的开邻域.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $U$
\end_inset

是以
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

为中心, 
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{\epsilon}{2}$
\end_inset

为半径的开球.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由于
\begin_inset Formula $d(x,A)=\inf_{a\in A}d(x,a)$
\end_inset

, 取
\begin_inset Formula $a\in A$
\end_inset

, s.t.
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
d(x,a)<d(x,A)+\frac{\epsilon}{2}.
\]

\end_inset

若
\begin_inset Formula $z\in U$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
d(z,A)\le d(z,a)\le d(z,x)+d(x,a)<\frac{\epsilon}{2}+d(x,A)+\frac{\epsilon}{2}=d(x,A)+\epsilon.
\]

\end_inset

同理
\begin_inset Formula $d(x,A)\le d(z,A)+\epsilon$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
所以
\begin_inset Formula $f(z)\in(d-\epsilon,d+\epsilon)$
\end_inset

, 即
\begin_inset Formula $\forall z\in U$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $z\in f^{-1}(d-\epsilon,d+\epsilon)$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
也即
\begin_inset Formula $U\subseteq f^{-1}(d-\epsilon,d+\epsilon)\subseteq f^{-1}(N)$
\end_inset

.
 故
\begin_inset Formula $f^{-1}(N)$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

的邻域.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
Lem.
 2.14.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $A,B$
\end_inset

是度量空间
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

中的两不交闭集, 则存在连续函数
\begin_inset Formula $f:X\to\RR$
\end_inset

, 使
\begin_inset Formula $f(B)=-1$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $f(A)=1$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $f(X\setminus(A\cup B))=(-1,1)$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
pf.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由
\begin_inset Formula $A,B$
\end_inset

为不交闭集, 故
\begin_inset Formula $\forall x\in X$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $d(x,A)+d(x,B)\ne0$
\end_inset

.
 则取
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f(x)=\frac{d(x,B)-d(x,A)}{d(x,B)+d(x,A)}.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
Lem.
 2.15.
 (Tietz扩张定理)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
在度量空间的闭子集上定义的任何连续实函数可扩张到整个空间.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
证明的关键部分: 定义
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
A_{1}=\left\{ x\in C:f(x)\ge\frac{M}{3}\right\} ;
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
B_{1}=\left\{ x\in C:f(x)\le-\frac{M}{3}\right\} ,
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $A_{1}\cap B_{1}=\varnothing$
\end_inset

, 且都在
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

中闭.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由Lem.
 2.14推出, 有连续映射
\begin_inset Formula $g_{1}:X\to\left[-\frac{M}{3},\frac{M}{3}\right]$
\end_inset

, s.t.
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
g_{1}(A_{1})=\frac{M}{3},\quad g_{1}(B_{1})=-\frac{M}{3},\quad g_{1}(X\setminus(A_{1}\cup B_{1}))=\left(-\frac{M}{3},\frac{M}{3}\right).
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\forall x\in C,\ \left|f(x)-g_{1}(x)\right|\le\frac{2M}{3}.
\]

\end_inset

定义
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
A_{2}=\left\{ x\in C:f(x)-g_{1}(x)\ge\frac{2M}{9}\right\} ;
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
B_{1}=\left\{ x\in C:f(x)-g_{1}(x)\le-\frac{2M}{9}\right\} ,
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $A_{2}\cap B_{2}=\varnothing$
\end_inset

, 且都在
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

中闭.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由Lem.
 2.14推出, 有连续映射
\begin_inset Formula $g_{2}:X\to\left[-\frac{2M}{9},\frac{2M}{9}\right]$
\end_inset

, s.t.
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
g_{2}(A_{2})=\frac{2M}{9},\quad g_{2}(B_{2})=-\frac{2M}{9},\quad g_{2}(X\setminus(A_{2}\cup B_{2}))=\left(-\frac{2M}{9},\frac{2M}{9}\right).
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\forall x\in C,\ \left|f(x)-g_{1}(x)-g_{2}(x)\right|\le\frac{4M}{9}.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
递归取极限得到
\begin_inset Formula $g(x)$
\end_inset

, 在
\begin_inset Formula $X\setminus C$
\end_inset

上
\begin_inset Formula $\left|g(x)\right|<M$
\end_inset

是因为: 因
\begin_inset Formula $C$
\end_inset

闭, 
\begin_inset Formula $g^{-1}(X\setminus C)$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $\RR$
\end_inset

中开, 所以娶不到等号.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
当
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

无界时的补充: 由于有界情况下的结论是
\begin_inset Formula $h\circ f:C\to\RR$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

上的延拓
\begin_inset Formula $g:X\to\RR$
\end_inset

仅在
\begin_inset Formula $X\setminus C$
\end_inset

上使
\begin_inset Formula $\left|g(x)\right|<1$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
而
\begin_inset Formula $g\mid_{C}=h\circ f\mid_{C}=(_{}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
newpage
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
printindex
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

